This is a django 1.5 implementation of a Burning Man site, developed for Bioluminati, a 50ish person camp of over 15 years.

This is intended to be an upgrade from the current site, which can be viewed at www.bioluminati.org. 

Goals of this project:

1. Allow for greater ease of meal signups [DONE]
2. Make it possible to easily view who has signed up for which shift [DONE}
2. Allow for chef to dictate how many kp's and sous chefs are needed for a meal [DONE]
3. Improved display of meal restrictions on a single page printable summary
4. Consolidate pages and elminate out of date information on site 
5. Dynamically generated random displays of camp photos 
6. Flesh out user profile and travel info


